==English==

===Etymology===
From {{m|en|geometric}} and {{m|en|-ian}}, presumably by analogy with other words in {{m|en|-ician}}, such as {{m|en|mathematician}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[geometer]]; a [[mathematician]] specializing in the study of [[geometry]].

